sequenceDiagram
    actor Agent
    participant API
    participant Auth as Token Auth
    participant Task as Task Service
    participant Claim as Claim Service
    participant Workflow as Workflow Engine
    participant Audit as Audit Log
    participant DB

    Agent->>API: POST /tasks
    API->>Auth: Validate agent token
    Auth-->>API: Token valid, scopes OK
    API->>Task: Create task
    Task->>DB: Save task
    Task->>Audit: Record task created
    Audit->>DB: Save event

    Agent->>API: POST /tasks/{id}/claim
    API->>Auth: Validate token + claim scope
    Auth-->>API: Allowed
    API->>Claim: Claim task
    Claim->>Workflow: Check claim rules
    Workflow-->>Claim: Claim allowed
    Claim->>DB: Save claim
    Claim->>Audit: Record claim event
    Audit->>DB: Save event
    API-->>Agent: Task claimed
